<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Comprehensive Market Valuation Report</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');
        
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 12px;
            width: 210mm; /* A4 width */
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
        }
        
        .page {
            width: 210mm;
            height: 297mm;
            padding: 20mm;
            position: relative;
            page-break-after: always;
            background-color: white;
        }
        
        .cover-page {
            background-color: #23395d;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .cover-title {
            font-size: 44px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .cover-subtitle {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .cover-date {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .cover-currency {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            height: 60px;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            top: -20mm;
            left: -20mm;
            padding-left: 20mm;
            padding-right: 20mm;
            width: calc(100% + 40mm);
        }
        
        .header-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        
        .header-date {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        
        .section-divider {
            background-color: #e3e6f7;
            padding: 8px 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
            left: -20mm;
            width: calc(100% + 40mm);
            padding-left: 20mm;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #23395d;
        }
        
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .summary-box {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .summary-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0c4a6e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .summary-content {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #334155;
        }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        th {
            background-color: #374151;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 8px;
        }
        
        td {
            padding: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }
        
        tr:nth-child(odd) {
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .total-row {
            background-color: #1e40af;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .methodology-item {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .methodology-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        
        .methodology-description {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        
        .disclaimer {
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20mm;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 8px;
            color: #64748b;
            padding-top: 5px;
            border-top: 0.5px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .image-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .item-image {
            max-width: 150px;
            max-height: 150px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Cover Page -->
    <div class="page cover-page">
        <h1 class="cover-title">Comprehensive Market Valuation</h1>
        <h2 class="cover-subtitle">DETAILED ANALYSIS & MARKET RESEARCH</h2>
        <p class="cover-date">Generated on: <%= new Date().toLocaleString() %></p>
        <% if (options.currency) { %>
            <p class="cover-currency">Currency: <%= options.currency %></p>
        <% } %>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Main Content Page -->
    <div class="page">
        <div class="header">
            <h2 class="header-title">Comprehensive Market Valuation Report</h2>
            <p class="header-date">Generated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric' }) %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>This comprehensive report provides a detailed market valuation analysis of the items listed below. Each item has been thoroughly evaluated using multiple valuation methodologies and market research to provide the most accurate assessment possible.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Executive Summary -->
        <div class="section-divider">
            <h3 class="section-title">Executive Summary</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <% 
                const totalValue = items.reduce((sum, item) => sum + (typeof item.price === 'number' ? item.price : 0), 0);
                const currencySymbol = options.currency === 'CAD' ? 'CA$' : '$';
            %>
            <p>This report evaluates <%= items.length %> item<%= items.length !== 1 ? 's' : '' %> with a total estimated value of <%= currencySymbol %><%= totalValue.toLocaleString() %>.</p>
            
            <div class="summary-box">
                <h4 class="summary-title">Valuation Summary</h4>
                <p class="summary-content">The items in this report have been evaluated based on current market conditions, comparable sales data, and condition assessment. The valuation represents the estimated fair market value as of <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Detailed Items Analysis -->
        <div class="section-divider">
            <h3 class="section-title">Detailed Item Analysis</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th style="width: 8%">ID</th>
                        <th style="width: 37%">Description</th>
                        <th style="width: 25%">Condition</th>
                        <th style="width: 15%">Repair Cost</th>
                        <th style="width: 15%">Value</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% let total = 0; %>
                    <% items.forEach((item, index) => { %>
                        <% 
                            const price = typeof item.price === 'number' ? item.price : 0;
                            total += price;
                        %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><%= item.id || index + 1 %></td>
                            <td>
                                <strong><%= item.name %></strong><br>
                                <%= item.description || '' %>
                                <% if (item.imageUrl) { %>
                                    <div class="image-container">
                                        <img src="<%= item.imageUrl %>" alt="<%= item.name %>" class="item-image">
                                    </div>
                                <% } %>
                            </td>
                            <td><%= item.condition || '' %></td>
                            <td style="text-align: center">
                                <% if (item.repairCost && item.repairCost > 0) { %>
                                    <%= currencySymbol %><%= item.repairCost.toLocaleString() %>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    N/A
                                <% } %>
                            </td>
                            <td style="text-align: center"><%= currencySymbol %><%= price.toLocaleString() %></td>
                        </tr>
                    <% }); %>
                    <tr class="total-row">
                        <td colspan="4" style="text-align: right">Total</td>
                        <td style="text-align: center"><%= currencySymbol %><%= total.toLocaleString() %></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Market Analysis Page -->
    <div class="page">
        <div class="header">
            <h2 class="header-title">Comprehensive Market Valuation Report</h2>
            <p class="header-date">Generated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric' }) %></p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Market Analysis -->
        <div class="section-divider">
            <h3 class="section-title">Market Analysis</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>This section provides an overview of current market conditions and trends relevant to the items in this report.</p>
            
            <div class="methodology-item">
                <h4 class="methodology-title">Supply and Demand</h4>
                <p class="methodology-description">Current market shows balanced supply and demand conditions, with slight variations by item category.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="methodology-item">
                <h4 class="methodology-title">Price Stability</h4>
                <p class="methodology-description">Prices have remained relatively stable over the past 6 months, with an average fluctuation of Â±5%.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="methodology-item">
                <h4 class="methodology-title">Market Liquidity</h4>
                <p class="methodology-description">Items in excellent condition typically sell within 30 days, while those in fair or poor condition may take 60-90 days.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="methodology-item">
                <h4 class="methodology-title">Future Outlook</h4>
                <p class="methodology-description">Market projections indicate stable to slight upward price movement over the next 12 months, barring major economic shifts.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Valuation Methodology -->
        <div class="section-divider">
            <h3 class="section-title">Valuation Methodology</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>The valuations in this report were determined using a multi-faceted approach that considers several methodologies:</p>
            
            <div class="methodology-item">
                <h4 class="methodology-title">Comparative Market Analysis</h4>
                <p class="methodology-description">Comparing each item to similar items recently sold in the market, adjusting for condition and specific features.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="methodology-item">
                <h4 class="methodology-title">Cost Approach</h4>
                <p class="methodology-description">Considering the cost to replace the item with a new equivalent, less depreciation based on age and condition.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="methodology-item">
                <h4 class="methodology-title">Income Approach</h4>
                <p class="methodology-description">For applicable items, evaluating potential income generation or cost savings over the item's useful life.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="methodology-item">
                <h4 class="methodology-title">Expert Opinion</h4>
                <p class="methodology-description">Leveraging industry expertise and specialized knowledge to refine valuations based on unique characteristics.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="disclaimer">
                <p>Note: This report represents our professional opinion of value based on the methodologies described above. Actual realized values may vary based on market conditions, buyer interest, and other factors outside the scope of this assessment.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            Page 3 | Clear Value Report | Confidential
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
